com.itko.lisa.remote

Interface IAgentInfo

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AgentInfo2

    public interface IAgentInfo
extends java.io.Serializable
    This interface encapsulates information about an agent that is then made public to all interested parties so they can later subscribe to this agent events or invoke APIs on it.
